In c079e29

`ConnectDirectly` and `ConnectThroughProxy` now differ in their primary args, with Directly taking a `CService` and Proxy remaining with `std::string&` (for host and port) which results in:

_src/net.cpp_

```cpp
        } else if (use_proxy) {
